cc:Work.dc:title: Snow Globe -Penguin with Umbrella
cc:Work.dc:description: A penguin attempting to stay out of the falling snow with an umbrella. Unfortunately for him he'll never leave the snow globe without a quick edit in Inkscape. This is a remix (Thanks Moini) partially...and thanks to Moini for pointing out to me that this is not a Panda in my first upload.. :)\nAlthough this graphic does not fall inside the rules of the coloring book competition since it is not a coloring book drawing I thought it was so cute I had to submit it.
